{"title":"Merida 2022 Scultura Team is lighter, more aero and includes wireless Shimano Dura-Ace 12 speed","link":"https://bikerumor.com/2021/09/01/meridas-2022-scultura-team-is-lighter-more-aero-and-comes-stock-with-wireless-shimano-dura-ace-12-speed/","date":1630507600000,"content":"<div id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"><div data-off-canvas-content=\"\"><main role=\"main\"><article id=\"post-269950\" role=\"article\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"http://schema.org/BlogPosting\"><header></header><section itemprop=\"text\"><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/31123702/Meridas-2022-Scultura-Team-side-full-bike-.jpeg\"><figure><img width=\"640\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/31123702/Meridas-2022-Scultura-Team-side-full-bike-.jpeg?ezimgfmt=rs%3Adevice%2Frscb28-1\" alt=\"Meridas 2022 Scultura Team side full bike\" loading=\"eager\" data-feature=\"1\" srcset=\"\" sizes=\"\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb28 src ng ngcb28 srcset\"></figure></a><p>Lighter, faster, and more comfortable — Merida claims its all-new 2022 Scultura Team is all that and more. Eagle-eyed viewers noticed a new frame under Mark Padun and Jack Haig (Team Bahrain-Victorious) at the 2021 Critérium du Dauphiné, and it’s garnered much attention. The massive number of victories the 2022 Scultura Team has amassed already; two stages in the Critérium du Dauphiné underneath Mark Padun, one in the Tour de France, ridden by Dylan Teuns, and one by Damiano Caruso in the Vuelta an España — we’re thinking Meridas telling the truth.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/31123657/Meridas-2022-Scultura-Team-winding-road-.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/31123657/Meridas-2022-Scultura-Team-winding-road-.jpeg?ezimgfmt=rs:640x427/rscb28/ng:webp/ngcb28\" alt=\"Meridas 2022 Scultura Team winding road\" width=\"640\" height=\"427\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/31123657/Meridas-2022-Scultura-Team-winding-road-.jpeg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb28 640w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/31123657/Meridas-2022-Scultura-Team-winding-road--297x198.jpeg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb28 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/31123657/Meridas-2022-Scultura-Team-winding-road--120x80.jpeg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb28 120w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb28 src ng ngcb28 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/31123657/Meridas-2022-Scultura-Team-winding-road-.jpeg?ezimgfmt=rs:640x427/rscb28/ng:webp/ngcb28\" ezoid=\"0.14122605964204604\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/31123657/Meridas-2022-Scultura-Team-winding-road-.jpeg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb28 640w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/31123657/Meridas-2022-Scultura-Team-winding-road--297x198.jpeg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb28 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/31123657/Meridas-2022-Scultura-Team-winding-road--120x80.jpeg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb28 120w\"></a></p><p>The 2022 version is the fifth generation of the <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2015/05/11/2016-merida-scultura-claims-to-be-lightest-production-road-bike-in-the-world/\">Scultura Team, initially launched in 2006 as the go-to lightweight climbing/all-around bike for world tour teams.</a> As the cycling universe leans towards a broader user base, the 2022 Scultura Team takes some hints from the 2021 <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2020/07/21/all-new-merida-scultura-endurance-finds-all-road-sweet-spot-between-gravel-road-racing/\">Scultura Endurance</a> make this ride much more than a climbing day machine.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/31123611/Meridas-2022-Scultura-Team-riding-.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/31123611/Meridas-2022-Scultura-Team-riding-.jpeg\" alt=\"Meridas 2022 Scultura Team riding\" width=\"640\" height=\"427\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/31123611/Meridas-2022-Scultura-Team-riding-.jpeg 640w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/31123611/Meridas-2022-Scultura-Team-riding--297x198.jpeg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/31123611/Meridas-2022-Scultura-Team-riding--120x80.jpeg 120w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb28 src ng ngcb28 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/31123611/Meridas-2022-Scultura-Team-riding-.jpeg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/31123611/Meridas-2022-Scultura-Team-riding-.jpeg 640w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/31123611/Meridas-2022-Scultura-Team-riding--297x198.jpeg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/31123611/Meridas-2022-Scultura-Team-riding--120x80.jpeg 120w\"></a></p><h2>What’s new — 2022 Scultura Team</h2><p>The 2022 Scultura Team is said to be faster than its predecessor — how? Well, Merida not only dropped the weight of the already super-light frame by 4.4% (860g to 822g), but they also took lots of inspiration from the <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2020/07/30/2021-merida-reacto-aero-road-bike-is-faster-more-comfortable-more-versatile-ready-for-any-race/\">Merida Reacto aero frame,</a> saving precious watts and still found room to fit a 30mm tire with ease, making it an all-around threat.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/31123639/Meridas-2022-Scultura-Team-logo-detail-.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/31123639/Meridas-2022-Scultura-Team-logo-detail-.jpeg\" alt=\"Meridas 2022 Scultura Team logo detail\" width=\"640\" height=\"427\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/31123639/Meridas-2022-Scultura-Team-logo-detail-.jpeg 640w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/31123639/Meridas-2022-Scultura-Team-logo-detail--297x198.jpeg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/31123639/Meridas-2022-Scultura-Team-logo-detail--120x80.jpeg 120w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb28 src ng ngcb28 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/31123639/Meridas-2022-Scultura-Team-logo-detail-.jpeg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/31123639/Meridas-2022-Scultura-Team-logo-detail-.jpeg 640w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/31123639/Meridas-2022-Scultura-Team-logo-detail--297x198.jpeg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/31123639/Meridas-2022-Scultura-Team-logo-detail--120x80.jpeg 120w\"></a></p><h2>2022 Scultura Team frame</h2><p>The 2022 Scultura Team moves to an entirely internal cable design, aesthetically pleasing and slippery in the wind. The new one-piece Merida Team SL bar/stem helps, available in a wide range of stem lengths (90-120 mm) and bar widths (400-440 mm), able to suit tons of riding styles and body types.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/31123650/Meridas-2022-Scultura-Team-stem-top-cap-.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/31123650/Meridas-2022-Scultura-Team-stem-top-cap-.jpeg\" alt=\"Meridas 2022 Scultura Team stem top cap\" width=\"640\" height=\"427\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/31123650/Meridas-2022-Scultura-Team-stem-top-cap-.jpeg 640w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/31123650/Meridas-2022-Scultura-Team-stem-top-cap--297x198.jpeg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/31123650/Meridas-2022-Scultura-Team-stem-top-cap--120x80.jpeg 120w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb28 src ng ngcb28 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/31123650/Meridas-2022-Scultura-Team-stem-top-cap-.jpeg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/31123650/Meridas-2022-Scultura-Team-stem-top-cap-.jpeg 640w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/31123650/Meridas-2022-Scultura-Team-stem-top-cap--297x198.jpeg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/31123650/Meridas-2022-Scultura-Team-stem-top-cap--120x80.jpeg 120w\"></a></p><p>Merida also looked to the long term and updated the 2022 Scultura Team with its new Force Diffuser steerer sleeve, which increases steerer tube durability and overall longevity.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/31123708/Meridas-2022-Scultura-Team-full-bar-stem-.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/31123708/Meridas-2022-Scultura-Team-full-bar-stem-.jpeg\" alt=\"Meridas 2022 Scultura Team full bar stem\" width=\"640\" height=\"427\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/31123708/Meridas-2022-Scultura-Team-full-bar-stem-.jpeg 640w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/31123708/Meridas-2022-Scultura-Team-full-bar-stem--297x198.jpeg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/31123708/Meridas-2022-Scultura-Team-full-bar-stem--120x80.jpeg 120w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb28 src ng ngcb28 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/31123708/Meridas-2022-Scultura-Team-full-bar-stem-.jpeg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/31123708/Meridas-2022-Scultura-Team-full-bar-stem-.jpeg 640w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/31123708/Meridas-2022-Scultura-Team-full-bar-stem--297x198.jpeg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/31123708/Meridas-2022-Scultura-Team-full-bar-stem--120x80.jpeg 120w\"></a></p><p>The 2022 Scultura Team frame takes a similar approach to seat stays as the Reacto, attaching lower on the frame but not dropped like other manufacturers or the Reacto. This aids in reduced drag but also keeps a very classic look on the 2022 Scultura Team.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/31123701/Meridas-2022-Scultura-Team-headset-.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/31123701/Meridas-2022-Scultura-Team-headset-.jpeg\" alt=\"Meridas 2022 Scultura Team headset\" width=\"640\" height=\"427\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/31123701/Meridas-2022-Scultura-Team-headset-.jpeg 640w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/31123701/Meridas-2022-Scultura-Team-headset--297x198.jpeg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/31123701/Meridas-2022-Scultura-Team-headset--120x80.jpeg 120w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb28 src ng ngcb28 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/31123701/Meridas-2022-Scultura-Team-headset-.jpeg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/31123701/Meridas-2022-Scultura-Team-headset-.jpeg 640w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/31123701/Meridas-2022-Scultura-Team-headset--297x198.jpeg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/31123701/Meridas-2022-Scultura-Team-headset--120x80.jpeg 120w\"></a></p><p>The headtube is nearly identical to the Reacto, a design feature that reduces drag, helps hide the cables and gives a nice nesting spot for the one-piece bar stem. The fork is broad, not only to support a larger tire but aid in aerodynamics.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/31123641/Meridas-2022-Scultura-Team-seatpost-.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/31123641/Meridas-2022-Scultura-Team-seatpost-.jpeg\" alt=\"Meridas 2022 Scultura Team seatpost\" width=\"640\" height=\"427\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/31123641/Meridas-2022-Scultura-Team-seatpost-.jpeg 640w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/31123641/Meridas-2022-Scultura-Team-seatpost--297x198.jpeg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/31123641/Meridas-2022-Scultura-Team-seatpost--120x80.jpeg 120w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb28 src ng ngcb28 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/31123641/Meridas-2022-Scultura-Team-seatpost-.jpeg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/31123641/Meridas-2022-Scultura-Team-seatpost-.jpeg 640w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/31123641/Meridas-2022-Scultura-Team-seatpost--297x198.jpeg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/31123641/Meridas-2022-Scultura-Team-seatpost--120x80.jpeg 120w\"></a></p><p>Compared to the previous generation, the 2022 Scultura Team gets a much stiffer pedaling platform via bottom bracket stiffness and lateral fork stiffness. Merida explains, “Compared to the previous Scultura, the bottom bracket stiffness is maintained at 62 N per mm of deflection, and lateral fork stiffness is up 12.8% to 53 N/mm.” What does this translate to for the rider? More bang for your buck when you push the pedals and higher precision steering all around.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/31123634/Meridas-2022-Scultura-Team-trakiung-a-drink-.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/31123634/Meridas-2022-Scultura-Team-trakiung-a-drink-.jpeg\" alt=\"Meridas 2022 Scultura Team t\" width=\"640\" height=\"427\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/31123634/Meridas-2022-Scultura-Team-trakiung-a-drink-.jpeg 640w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/31123634/Meridas-2022-Scultura-Team-trakiung-a-drink--297x198.jpeg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/31123634/Meridas-2022-Scultura-Team-trakiung-a-drink--120x80.jpeg 120w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb28 src ng ngcb28 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/31123634/Meridas-2022-Scultura-Team-trakiung-a-drink-.jpeg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/31123634/Meridas-2022-Scultura-Team-trakiung-a-drink-.jpeg 640w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/31123634/Meridas-2022-Scultura-Team-trakiung-a-drink--297x198.jpeg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/31123634/Meridas-2022-Scultura-Team-trakiung-a-drink--120x80.jpeg 120w\"></a></p><h2>How about that comfort?</h2><p>Comfort can take a 100-mile ride from a death march to a fun exploration, and the World Tour can be the difference between winning and losing. The 2022 Scultura Team takes another page from the Scultura Endurance and reduces the vertical stiffness from the saddle to the bottom bracket. Taking the previous models 111 N/mm to well below 80 N/mm, near the endurance range. Merida achieved this by shortening the seat tube by around 40mm, exposing more seatpost, allowing for natural compliance. The 30mm wide tires are a huge help in the range, paired with generously wide Vision Metron wheels.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/31123616/Meridas-2022-Scultura-Team-riding-in-the-drops-.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/31123616/Meridas-2022-Scultura-Team-riding-in-the-drops-.jpeg\" alt=\"Meridas 2022 Scultura Team riding in the drops\" width=\"640\" height=\"427\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/31123616/Meridas-2022-Scultura-Team-riding-in-the-drops-.jpeg 640w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/31123616/Meridas-2022-Scultura-Team-riding-in-the-drops--297x198.jpeg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/31123616/Meridas-2022-Scultura-Team-riding-in-the-drops--120x80.jpeg 120w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb28 src ng ngcb28 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/31123616/Meridas-2022-Scultura-Team-riding-in-the-drops-.jpeg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/31123616/Meridas-2022-Scultura-Team-riding-in-the-drops-.jpeg 640w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/31123616/Meridas-2022-Scultura-Team-riding-in-the-drops--297x198.jpeg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/31123616/Meridas-2022-Scultura-Team-riding-in-the-drops--120x80.jpeg 120w\"></a></p><h2>2022 Merida Scultura Team Geometry</h2><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/31124442/M