ew Metron 45SL wider tubeless-ready wheels,</a> and all the high-end trimmings.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/31123636/Meridas-2022-Scultura-Team-shimano-Dura-are-wireless-.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/31123636/Meridas-2022-Scultura-Team-shimano-Dura-are-wireless-.jpeg\" alt=\"Meridas 2022 Scultura Team shimano Dura are wireless\" width=\"640\" height=\"427\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/31123636/Meridas-2022-Scultura-Team-shimano-Dura-are-wireless-.jpeg 640w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/31123636/Meridas-2022-Scultura-Team-shimano-Dura-are-wireless--297x198.jpeg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/31123636/Meridas-2022-Scultura-Team-shimano-Dura-are-wireless--120x80.jpeg 120w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb28 src ng ngcb28 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/31123636/Meridas-2022-Scultura-Team-shimano-Dura-are-wireless-.jpeg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/31123636/Meridas-2022-Scultura-Team-shimano-Dura-are-wireless-.jpeg 640w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/31123636/Meridas-2022-Scultura-Team-shimano-Dura-are-wireless--297x198.jpeg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/31123636/Meridas-2022-Scultura-Team-shimano-Dura-are-wireless--120x80.jpeg 120w\"></a></p><h2>Full Specs — 2022 Merida Scultura Team</h2><ul><li>CF5 frame (822 g in size M)</li><li>CF5 fork (389 g in size M)</li><li>New Shimano Dura-Ace 12s Di2 incl. power meter</li><li>New VISION METRON 45 SL tubeless ready</li><li>MERIDA TEAM SL 1P cockpit</li><li>Prologo SCRATCH M5 saddle with carbon rails</li><li>New Continental 5000S 28 mm</li><li>Direct mount rear derailleur for improved shifting</li><li>Disc coolers for improved head dispensation on long</li><li>12 mm through axles front and rear</li><li>Size-specific stem length and bar width</li></ul><p><strong>Price: $10,700 | £7,750 | €9,999</strong></p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/31123654/Meridas-2022-Scultura-Team-dura-ace-12-speed-crankset-.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/31123654/Meridas-2022-Scultura-Team-dura-ace-12-speed-crankset-.jpeg\" alt=\"Meridas 2022 Scultura Team dura ace 12 speed crankset\" width=\"640\" height=\"427\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/31123654/Meridas-2022-Scultura-Team-dura-ace-12-speed-crankset-.jpeg 640w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/31123654/Meridas-2022-Scultura-Team-dura-ace-12-speed-crankset--297x198.jpeg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/31123654/Meridas-2022-Scultura-Team-dura-ace-12-speed-crankset--120x80.jpeg 120w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb28 src ng ngcb28 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/31123654/Meridas-2022-Scultura-Team-dura-ace-12-speed-crankset-.jpeg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/31123654/Meridas-2022-Scultura-Team-dura-ace-12-speed-crankset-.jpeg 640w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/31123654/Meridas-2022-Scultura-Team-dura-ace-12-speed-crankset--297x198.jpeg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/31123654/Meridas-2022-Scultura-Team-dura-ace-12-speed-crankset--120x80.jpeg 120w\"></a></p><h2>Availability</h2><p>As of right now, there is no clear time of when the 2022 Scultura Team will be available for purchase, or if lower models of the frameset (other than the CF5) will be available for purchase. If you’ve been following the lead times in the industry you know this bike’s availability could fluctuate depending on the supply chain for component manufactures. If you’re frothing at the mouth for one like we are, we suggest checking out the <a href=\"https://www.merida-bikes.com/en\">Merida site</a> and signing up for notifications.</p></section></article></main></div></div>","author":"Jordan Villella","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"bb6f7b07c404572de4fe5752076847fc73c94d21dbb101cedf29ccee70532507","category":"Cycling"}